      • getDemoText

        public java.lang.String getDemoText()
        Description copied from interface: ColorSettingsPage
        Returns the text shown in the preview pane. If some elements need to be highlighted in the preview text which are not highlighted by the syntax highlighter, they need to be surrounded by XML-like tags, for example: <class>MyClass</class>. The mapping between the names of the tags and the text attribute keys used for highlighting is defined by the ColorSettingsPage.getAdditionalHighlightingTagToDescriptorMap() method.
        Specified by:
        getDemoText in interface ColorSettingsPage
        Returns:
        the text to show in the preview pane.
